{"tid":992845,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"派$4000計劃涉3億行政費　陳茂波指金額合理","createTime":"2019-01-23T13:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T13:24:36.000Z","uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ae3e660cb753d409466935e34bd2c6eb9e480254","tid":992845,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSxZh9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSxZh9P.jpg&h=12c709b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府向立法會遞交《2018年撥款條例草案》文件顯示，4000港元選擇性派錢計劃明年2月接受申請。財政司司長陳茂波今早(21日)出席活動後表示，該計劃有3個月申請期，明年4月應有首批市民收到款項，初步估算最多300萬人受惠。因計劃涉聘請及培訓人手，並要更新電腦系統做準備，以處理市民稅單和物業，有關準備工夫涉時數個月。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波指，今次計劃涉及行政費約3億港元，佔計劃開支3%，因計劃性質具針對性，要符合一定條件，故有一定手續，認為有關行政費用合理。連同行政費在內，計劃涉款約110多億港元，他認為是用得其所，重申資源用得準確些會較好，亦合乎今屆政府理財哲學。預計整個計劃工作應於明年完成。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/bkn-20180421112831587-0421_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180421%2Fbkn-20180421112831587-0421_00822_001.html&d=Mxbo3%2FVMs1bg%2BUg7vhJb8%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=233cef50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/bkn-20180421112831587-0421_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e72817b86808a3bf36705618bcc0248af0f702c","tid":992845,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:03:42.000Z","msg":"津貼$4000, 成本$200"},{"pid":"bb541e541415043cad3c5184c4919c9d186d21dc","tid":992845,"uid":99420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:07:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf2e91d0efde2341bf66d3d5338d261f75fd999a","tid":992845,"uid":35656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T13:08:55.000Z"